Some tricks:
    new LocalDateTime(t.getTime()).toDateTime(DateTime.UTC)    <-  server should be setup with UTC timezone
    new LocalDateTime(t.getTime(), DateTime.UTC).toDateTime()  <-  server timezone doesn't matter
